This is an Expo (React Native) app with Expo Router.

- Use path aliases (`@/`) for imports.
- Routes in `app/` are thin — delegate to `src/screens/`.
- `src/services/` has NO React Native imports. Only `src/platform/` touches native code.
- Do NOT touch `ios/` or `android/` directly — they're generated by Expo.
- Changes to `app.config.ts` or native deps require EAS Build (~15-25 min). JS-only changes ship via EAS Update (seconds).
- Run `pnpm lint && pnpm typecheck` before finishing.
